cdata.name: ATB coin
cdata.desc: ATB coin is a Proof of Stake cryptocurrency designed to solve some of the most pressing issues in the current crypto landscape, such as scalability, energency efficiency and more. ATB coin features some of the most recent technologies in the blockchain space such as the SegWit update and Lightning Network making it moreefficient, flexible, and agile. ATB coincomes with an array of lightweight and user-friendly walletsfor desktop, iOS, Android, and web.
